Bike Rental Management System 🚲

A Python-based bike rental management system that allows users to rent bikes, calculate rental charges, apply discounts, and generate receipts.

This project demonstrates Object-Oriented Programming concepts using Python.

---

Features

✅ Rent bikes  
✅ Hourly rental calculation  
✅ Discount support  
✅ Late return penalty  
✅ Receipt generation  
✅ Inventory tracking  

---

Tech Stack

- Python
- OOP (Object-Oriented Programming)

---

Project Structure

```bash
bike-rental-management-system/
│── finalcode.py
│── README.md
```

---
 Functionalities

Customer
- Rent bikes
- View bill
- Get receipt

Admin
- Manage stock
- Track rentals

